message:
No `lead_form_submitted` RUM action in the last 7 days. The submit handler isn't firing — either no real submissions are happening, or `track(events.lead_form_submitted, …)` in `src/components/ui/LeadForm.tsx` is no longer being reached.

Check end-to-end: visit https://revenuepoint.com/contact, fill the form, submit. Confirm a Lead lands in revenuepoint--prod within seconds. If the action fires but no Lead lands, the Web-to-Lead config has drifted (OID, field IDs, or reCAPTCHA keyname).

